---
// A 12-pixel tall horizontal stripe at the top of every page, stacked
// saffron / white / India green per the Indian national flag. The flag
// is a national symbol, not a party emblem — the brief's non-partisan
// rule is preserved.
//
// Token values live in src/styles/global.css under --color-flag-*.
// The visible white band is a thin hairline so it doesn't disappear on
// the warm Newsprint paper.
---

<div
  aria-hidden="true"
  class="flex h-3 w-full flex-col"
  data-tiranga
>
  <span class="h-1 bg-flag-saffron"></span>
  <span class="h-1 bg-flag-white"></span>
  <span class="h-1 bg-flag-green"></span>
</div>
